arts.ttl: Trialist bags brace for Colchester United under-21s in win over Swansea City
arts.sum: Swansea then went close when Morgan Bates drove a shot wide, following good play by substitute Aimar Govea. Swansea came agonisingly close to taking the lead on five minutes when Ramon Rees-Siso's header crashed against the crossbar, following Morgan Bates' cross from the left.
